cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.CY 

This paper focuses on the automated extraction and classification of visualizations from the web, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of machine learning algorithms for classification also suggests a connection to databases (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the emphasis on user preferences and tool design may relate to the field of cybernetics (cs.CY).
